    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so if it's such a design error, what about the people who argue that the veto is actually the only reason the UN even exists? like, they say without it, the big powers would just leave and the whole thing would collapse. is that seen as a valid point or just an excuse for why it doesn't work?",
